LLM Providers
LLM providers are organizations or entities that offer large language models for various applications, contributing to system functionalities like those of LightRAG.

Python
Python is a high-level programming language used widely for various applications, including the development of libraries like LightRAG.

OpenAI
OpenAI is a research organization that provides large language models (LLMs) that can be integrated into various applications, including those built with LightRAG.

Knowledge Graphs
Knowledge graphs are structured representations of information that enable effective storage and retrieval of data in systems like LightRAG.

LightRAG
LightRAG is a Python library designed for creating Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) systems, utilizing knowledge graphs for efficient information storage and retrieval.

Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG)
Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) refers to a framework for enhancing machine learning models with external data retrieval capabilities.
